    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1862-04-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1862-04-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="691"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d691">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr. De
                        Long</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 2.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1862-04-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 3, 1862.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> Your despatch of the 20th February (No. 3) has
                    been received.</p>
                <p>It gives an account of the arrest of two of the crew of the pirate Sumter, and
                    their detention, with a view of their being sent to the United States.</p>
                <p>I have subsequently learned, though informally, that the persons thus arrested
                    have been despatched to this country.</p>
                <p>The French minister residing at this capital mentioned to me, informally,
                    yesterday, that he was charged with a communication to me upon the same subject
                    by his government.</p>
                <p>For this reason I defer presenting the matter to the notice of the President
                    until the promised statement of Mr. Thouvenel shall have been received.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">James De Long,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>,<hi rend="italic"> Tangier.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
